OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1777327868
OL,3,CSouthern Water admits sewage pollution
OL,4,Cwhich occurred weeks after record fine
OL,6,FSouthern Water has admitted releasing
OL,7,Fraw sewage into the sea in a series of
OL,8,Fpollution incidents across parts of
OL,9,Fnorth Kent.
OL,11,FThe company admitted to releasing the
OL,12,Funtreated sewage, diesel and waste at
OL,13,Fvarious times between 2019 and 2021.
OL,15,FSome of the cases happened
OL,16,Fsimultaneously at different locations
OL,17,F- and weeks after the firm was handed
OL,18,Fa record #90 million fine for almost
OL,19,F7000 previous illegal discharges.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/7
