OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1777327868
OL,3,CSouthern Water admits sewage pollution
OL,4,Cwhich occurred weeks after record fine
OL,6,FIn July 2019, people reported seeing
OL,7,Fand smelling oil in Swalecliffe Brook
OL,8,Fin Whitstable.
OL,10,FEnvironment Agency staff were sent to
OL,11,Fthe scene, and discovered diesel from
OL,12,FSouthern Water's local wastewater
OL,13,Ftreatment plant.
OL,15,FIt got into the brook and then the
OL,16,Fsea, when a generator failed and began
OL,17,Fleaking. The public were warned to
OL,18,Fkeep themselves and their pets out of
OL,19,Fthe water.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
