FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1777327868
OL,3,CSouthern Water admits sewage pollution
OL,4,Cwhich occurred weeks after record fine
OL,6,FShortly before the start of the
OL,7,Fpandemic in 2020, untreated sewage was
OL,8,Freleased into Faversham Creek from a
OL,9,Fseparate wastewater station after
OL,10,Fpumps stopped working.
OL,12,FOn the same day, Swalecliffe Brook in
OL,13,FWhitstable was hit again, this time
OL,14,Fwith sewage, like the diesel, carried
OL,15,Finto the sea.
OL,17,FThen in October 2020, an almost
OL,18,Fidentical incident where sewage and
OL,19,Fother matter travelled out of the main
OL,20,Fgate of the works, along Brook Road,
OL,21,Facross the verge and into the brook.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
