OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1777327868
OL,3,CSouthern Water admits sewage pollution
OL,4,Cwhich occurred weeks after record fine
OL,6,FMore pollution happened at Southern
OL,7,FWater plants in Whitstable, in August
OL,8,F2021, and then again the beleaguered
OL,9,FSwalecliffe Brook had untreated sewage
OL,10,Fpouring into it on 6 August.
OL,11,FInvestigators found between around 70
OL,12,Fdead fish, including eels.
OL,14,FSigns were put up along beaches at
OL,15,FTankerton and Herne Bay, warning
OL,16,Fagainst swimming for nearly a week
OL,17,Fafterwards.
OL,19,FSouthern Water pleaded guilty at
OL,20,FMedway magistrates' court on 7 April
OL,21,Fto all five charges.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
