PN,41305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1777327868
OL,3,CSouthern Water admits sewage pollution
OL,4,Cwhich occurred weeks after record fine
OL,6,FSentencing will take place at the same
OL,7,Fcourt on a date to be confirmed.
OL,9,FDawn Theaker, the Environment Agency's
OL,10,Fwater industry regulation manager in
OL,11,Fthe South East, said: "All of these
OL,12,Fpollution incidents could have been
OL,13,Favoided if Southern Water had managed
OL,14,Foperations more carefully, and had in
OL,15,Fplace the necessary checks to deal
OL,16,Fwith problems when they occurred.
OL,26,@sD@WOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/7
