PN,41306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1777327868
OL,3,CSouthern Water admits sewage pollution
OL,4,Cwhich occurred weeks after record fine
OL,6,F"It's a familiar pattern with water
OL,7,Fcompanies. Always catching up with
OL,8,Fevents. The Environment Agency will
OL,9,Fkeep Southern Water in its sights with
OL,10,Fmore inspections, even tougher
OL,11,Fregulation and prosecution in the most
OL,12,Fserious cases.
OL,14,F"Anyone who suspects pollution in our
OL,15,Frivers and seas is urged to contact
OL,16,Fthe Environment Agency's 24-hour
OL,17,Fincident hotline: 0800 807060."
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOUyD@_O]
